				<td colspan="2"><span>I have a question about the Boastful Bellow AAs. I’m a puller and I’m just about to spend 6 points on Boastful Bellow but I want to make sure I’m doing the right thing.
<br />

<br />
My question is, do the other BB AAs just extend the damage of this one? Or are they their own Bellows, meaning I could potentially have 3 bellows to use? 
<br />

<br />
My assumption is that the bellow just gets more powerful. If this is the case, what kind of damage would you get if you had Boastful Bellow, Exultant Bellowing, and Fortified Bellowing?
<br />
</span></td>
