			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>They increase the damage AND they increase the max level at which the stun can hit.  With the basic Boastful Bellow, the max level you can stun is 60.  Exultant Bellow increases that level by 1 per level of EB. 
<br />

<br />
The actvate number for Exultant Bellow is a different number from the earlier Boastful Bellow.  I am told they are on the same timer so you cannot use both, though I have never actually made up multiple hotkeys and tested it.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
