				<td colspan="2"><span>You'll want to switch your hotkey to the appropriate one for Exultant Bellow.  The AA that adds a chance of critting on DoTs is Critical Affliction.  Level one of that seems to add about a 3% chance of getting a double damage crit.
<br />

<br />
Bellow is a great pulling tool and the ability to stun a caster to try to convince it to actually come on the pull instead of standing there mana dumping can be handy.  But as Moose said, getting enough levels of it to stun the stuff you are fighting at 65+ is expensive.</span></td>
